            <p><a href="/about-dr-lavian/">Dr. Lavian&rsquo;s</a> extensive experience with streaming protocols, audio/video conferencing, and streaming technologies, primarily implemented through the TCP/IP protocol suite, gives him a keen understanding of the logic behind streaming and its component application, transport, network, data link, and physical layers.</p>
